{"tid":1379014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全面罷工 一定要配合地鐵不合作 / 車長罷工","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:32:10.000Z","uid":221856,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e3cc42b245aca41a210a747ba1108b0bbff62f","tid":1379014,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"好多好多30-40歲既同路人<br />\n遊行會出黎, 物資會幫手買, 眾籌會比大大份<br />\n但真係有家庭負擔, 每個月唔少開支<br />\n罷工對佢地黎講係有難度的, 尤其佢地既上司9成廢老藍絲<br />\n<br />\n唔好講長期, 就算一日<br />\n係全城話罷工既日子佢罷工, 已經等於表左態<br />\n所以要比個藉口佢地唔返工, 一定要配合地鐵不合作/車長罷工 <br />\n唔係之前1-2粒鐘果隻, 真係長時間果隻先得<br />\n<br />\n客觀講, 我地呢啲後生, 雖然人多去罷工, 但我地好多都係低級員工, 象徵意義比實際意義大<br />\n要遍地開花 一定要有埋佢地既參與"},{"pid":"92d3708fb3383d2617b24255516d4fa9d896e318","tid":1379014,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9103540ec5702f98beede60d95b089f596fdbabb","tid":1379014,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b288afae94269d9c307191b026f53d5b18f71fb5","tid":1379014,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:23:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b62eedcbad06f1fe1e582e4d579cb3f116f5c51","tid":1379014,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"727 278 警狗打人合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6N677ZNEHyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6N677ZNEHyo&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyyxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=e1ffc3ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6N677ZNEHyo</a>"},{"pid":"265440847cad2028965eeaa499e8750378154a20","tid":1379014,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7月30日地鐵不合作運動 8月5日香港大罷工！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"01fa8f6129360ec4b582c3d7f25d58a9a350a4af","tid":1379014,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco